OL,3,CWorkers take to picket lines in strike
OL,4,Caction
OL,6,FNorthern Ireland Secretary Chris
OL,7,FHeaton-Harris has been urged to
OL,8,Frelease funding to make delayed pay
OL,9,Fawards in the absence of a functioning
OL,10,Fdevolved government.
OL,12,FHe has refused, saying the matter is
OL,13,Ffor the devolved Assembly.
OL,15,FThe UK Government has offered a
OL,16,Ffinancial package worth more than
OL,17,F#3billion to accompany the return of a
OL,18,Fdevolved Executive in Belfast.
OL,20,FA portion of which has been ringfenced
OL,21,Ffor public sector pay awards.
