OL,3,CWorkers take to picket lines in strike
OL,4,Caction
OL,6,F"A few years ago, these workers were
OL,7,Fbeing hailed as frontline heroes. They
OL,8,Fdeserve better and they are ready and
OL,9,Fwilling to strike to secure it.
OL,11,F"At any point, if a meaningful pay
OL,12,Foffer is received then that is
OL,13,Fsomething our members will consider
OL,14,Fand respond to appropriately but in
OL,15,Fthe absence of any movement we have no
OL,16,Falternative but to proceed with the
OL,17,Fplanned action."
